Use BooleanQuery to combine multiple Queries:

BooleanQuery query = new BooleanQuery();
query.add(new TermQuery(new Term("type", "stockSingle")), true, false);
query.add(new TermQuery(new Term("seqNo", "1000")), true, false);
...

-----Original Message-----
