I am using 6 indexers / indexes to balance the speed of indexing against =
query performance for 40+ million documents.  I came to this number =
through trial and error, and performance testing on the indexing side =
with a fast 4 processor machine.  The trick is to max out the I/O =
throughput.

-Will

