Lucene 1.4 changed the file format for indexes. You can access a old =
index
using lucene 1.4 but you can't access index which was created using =
lucene
1.4 with older versions.
I suggest you rebuild your index using lucene 1.4

Aviran
http://aviran.mordos.com

